FEAT. &amp; AUTH - Authorizations, and system features. Check here to 
               see if Call trace OR caller ID is active. 
 
FEATURE TIMERS - This is a bit interesting. 
                 EXAMPLE:
                        *  (1 unit =1.0  sec)
                        ** (1 unit =0.1  sec)
                        ***(1 unit =0.01 sec)
                        *AUTO_REDIAL-  30  
