                                MAGNETO_AUTO_ANS-    30  
                                CF_NO_ANS- 200  
 
SYSTEM GEN - MENU:
                (SYSGEN)
                0-INSTALL
                1-SIZES_DEF
                2-SIZES_TAB
                3-SPEED_CALLS (MCC only)
                4-MUSIC
                5-TIME_SLOTS (4GC only)
