SYSTEM FEATURES - Trunk_calls_incoming, station_options, intercept/
                  incomplete, call_forwarding, camp_on, hotel,messaging, 
                  tones, diagnosrics, ISDN, network, and wireless
TONE PLAN - EXAMPLE:
~~~~~~~~
